org.apache.beam.runners.flink.metrics

Class ReaderInvocationUtil<OutputT,ReaderT extends Source.Reader<OutputT>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.runners.flink.metrics.ReaderInvocationUtil<OutputT,ReaderT>

  • public class ReaderInvocationUtil<OutputT,ReaderT extends Source.Reader<OutputT>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Util for invoking Source.Reader methods that might require a MetricsContainerImpl to be active. Source.Reader decorator which registers MetricsContainerImpl. It update metrics to Flink metric and accumulator in start and advance.
